A PAL Compiler for CMPUT 415.

Team Meow
- Steve Jahns
- Mike Armstrong
- Chris Pavlicek
- Connor Moreside

To build, run:

	$ make

from the root dir, which will place the pal compiler executable at
	
	./bin/pal

and asc interpreter executable at

	./bin/asc

and supporting library (with builtin routines) at 

	./bin/meowlib.asc

NOTE: Moving the generated pal executable to a different directory that
does not contain the asc interpreter or the meowlib.asc library will cause 
pal to fail.

To build and run all tests:

	$ make test

To build and run specific test suites:
	
	$ make ScannerTest
	$ make ParserTest
	$ make ParserTestWithFiles
	$ make MeowlibTest
	$ make CodegenTest

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PAL Sources
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	./src/main.cpp
		- driver program for compiler class

	./src/Compiler.cpp
	./src/Compiler.hpp
		- main compiler class

	./src/pal.lex
		- flex lexer source

	./src/Scanner.hpp
		- wrapper class for combined lexer + parser

	./src/pal.y
		- bison parser source

	./src/Parser.cpp
	./src/Parser.hpp
		- wrapper class for combined lexer + parser

	./src/Error.cpp
	./src/Error.hpp
		- error representation

	./src/ErrorCodes.hpp
		- defines all error types the compiler can find

	./src/ErrorManager.cpp
	./src/ErrorManager.hpp
		- tracks errors through the course of the compiler's execution

	./SymbolTable.cpp
	./SymbolTable.hpp
		- symbol table - tracks correspondences of names to constants, 
			types, variables, procedures and functions

	./EntryList.cpp
	./EntryList.hpp
		- entry in symbol table for a specific name, has a list of 
			symbols corresponding to the name, in order of 
			lexical level.

	./Symbol.cpp
	./Symbol.hpp
		- entry in symbol table entry list, represents a constant,
			type, variable, procedure or function definition

	./Type.cpp
	./Type.hpp
		- representation of type. Used by symbol to
		denote it's variable / constant type, array type, function return
		type, etc.

	./SemanticHelper.cpp
	./SemanticHelper.hpp
		- helper class used by parser for semantic analysis.

	./AscHelper.cpp
	./AscHelper.hpp
		- helper class used by parser for code generation.

	./AuxiliaryTypes.hpp
		- assorted types used for return values in parser rules, semantic 
		analysis, and symbol definitions

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Testing Sources
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	./test/ParserTest.cpp
		- PalParser unit tests

	./test/ScannerTest.cpp
		- PalScanner unit tests

	./test/ParserTestWithFiles.cpp
		- Full parser tests, generated by ./test/scripts/test_gen

	./test/SymbolTableTest.cpp
		- Unit tests for symbol table
		
	./test/MockScanner.cpp
		- Mock scanner class for PalParser unit tests

	./test/MockScanner.cpp
		- Mock scanner class for PalParser unit tests

	./test/test_cases/*
		- Test PAL programs (files starting with b are invalid programs,
			v are valid)

	./test/test_cases/cp3tests/*
		- Test PAL programs for checkpoint 3 submission

